'''Emojis''' are icons that can be summoned in front of a user to express themselves. 

While VRChat provides a set of default Emojis, users can purchase emojis within the [[Shop]] or users with a [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] subscription can upload images to use as Custom Emojis. Emojis can be spawned via the [[Special:MyLanguage/Action Menu#Emojis & Stickers|Action Menu]] or the Emoji [[Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu#Wings|Wing]] and managed on the [[Inventory]] page.

==Default emojis==
Default emojis are a set of 66 Emojis split into 4 pages of general emojis, accessibility emojis, summer emojis, fall emojis, and winter emojis.

