== Premium emoji and effects==

=== Premium Emoji ===
Premium Emoji are bigger, and more animated type of emoji. 

This type of emoji are labelled with "Premium" icon in the top right corner of the preview image on the inventory page and while viewing details of the emoji, there is a "Premium" label beside the preview button. Premium Emoji is affected by the "Animated Emoji" [[Trust and Safety#Shield Levels|safety]] setting.
<gallery mode="packed" heights="64">
File:PremiumIcon.png|Premium Icon
File:PremiumLabel.png|Premium Label
</gallery>

=== Emoji Effects ===
Emoji effects are effects that are visible on the emoji, these are applied to Exclusive, or Shop stickers to distinguish itself from Custom Stickers. This type of emoji can be filtered on the inventory page.

Known emoji effects include "Holographic".

* Holographic: applies a sheen, with a unique texture overlaying the emoji.

